Police are out in full force in Diepsloot following violent protests. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - A child has been killed after being hit by a bus in Diepsloot. An eyewitness said the child was crushed to death after the driver had closed the bus door. "...They were fighting to get into the bus and the bus driver closed the door and while the door was closed she tried to jump into the bus but it was too late for her and she stepped by the two tyres at the back," said the pupil. Meanwhile, residents in the area are protesting and demanding illegal foreign nationals leave the area. They claim the foreigners are responsible for several murders. Police are out in full force in Diepsloot following violent protests. Courtesy #DStv403